~Topic=Stem Matrix

~Format-,ADoc-
Hypercomplex multiplication formula:
Let h1 = x1 + y1i + z1j + w1k and h2 = x2 + y2i + z2j + w2k.
Then  h1h2 =  1(x1x2 - y1y2 - z1z2 + w1w2) +
              i(y1x2 + x1y2 - w1z2 - z1w2) +
              j(z1x2 - w1y2 + x1z2 - y1w2) +
              k(w1x2 + z1y2 + y1z2 + x1w2)
~ADoc+,Doc-,Online-
Hypercomplex multiplication formula:
Let stem:[h_1 = x_1 + y_1 i + z_1 j + w_1 k] and stem:[h_2 = x_2 + y_2 i + z_2 j + w_2 k].
Then

[stem]
++++
\{:
(h_1 h_2,=,(x_1 x_2 - y_1 y_2 - z_1 z_2 + w_1 w_2) +),
(,,         i(y_1 x_2 + x_1 y_2 - w_1 z_2 - z_1 w_2) +),
(,,         j(z_1 x_2 - w_1 y_2 + x_1 z_2 - y_1 w_2) +),
(,,         k(w_1 x_2 + z_1 y_2 + y_1 z_2 + x_1 w_2))
:\}
++++
~Doc+,Online+,Format+
